<div>The traditional way to do this stuff in MPI is&nbsp;</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>If rank==0 do_master_stuff</div>
<div>Else do_slave_stuff</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Sounds like that pattern should apply to your app.&nbsp;</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Pvm has been dead for years.&nbsp;<br>
<br>
